<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Our Services - Carpooling</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-image: url(services.jpg);
            background-size: cover;
            text-align: center;
            
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
            
        }

        .services-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-around;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .service-card {
            background-color: white;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 10px;
            width: 300px;
            margin: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .service-card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .service-card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .service-card h2 {
            margin: 10px;
            font-size: 1.5em;
            color: #007BFF;
        }

        .service-card p {
            margin: 10px;
            color: #555;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>Our Services</h1>
<div class="services-container">
    <div class="service-card">
        <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Carpool Matching">
        <h2>Carpool Matching</h2>
        <p>We connect commuters with similar routes to reduce travel costs and promote sustainable transportation.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card">
        <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Ride Scheduling">
        <h2>Ride Scheduling</h2>
        <p>Schedule your rides in advance and never worry about last-minute arrangements.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card">
        <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Incentives for Carpooling">
        <h2>Incentives for Carpooling</h2>
        <p>Get rewards like preferential parking and toll discounts when you share rides with others.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card">
        <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSZjJJcFFaDWN629VQJgMejEoETVJ_li_NsRQ&s" alt="Real-Time Updates">
        <h2>Real-Time Updates</h2>
        <p>Receive notifications about your ride, including real-time traffic updates and changes.</p>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>